 ('152', '152', 'en_us', 'Set up a Parking Citation Alert', 'Sign up for alerts', '', 'https://wmq1.etimspayments.com/pbw/include/vpportal/oakland/login_page.jsp', '<p>Parking citation alerts provide notifications to help manage your parking needs and avoid unnecessary penalties. When you create an account, it will alert you so you receive notifications about:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>When a new citation is issued to your vehicle</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>Before a penalty are applied</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>After a mail-in payment is applied</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>About upcoming hearings</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>Before you become “Boot Eligible”</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>Upcoming Resident Parking Permit Renewal</p>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    <p>City of Oakland Parking announcements</p></li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-12-18 23:08:02', '2016-01-07 00:52:21', '1093efcd-b938-4a7f-ab26-567a53766b28'),
