 ('412', '412', 'en_us', 'City Employee Pay Ranges', 'Download the Salary information sheet (pdf)', '', 'http://www2.oaklandnet.com/w/OAK032236', '<p>City Employees receive a range of pay based on their position and band. A full list of salary information is available to download.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', '[]', NULL, NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-07 00:56:42', '2016-01-07 00:56:42', 'd91b3048-c46f-43bb-8225-c53551fa4990'),
